<div class="projects">
  <div class="projects-header">
    <h3>Projects</h3>
    <%= image_tag "images/devices.png", class: "avatar-large", id: "projects-img" %>
  </div>
  <div class="card-wrapper">
    <div class="flip-container" ontouchstart="this.classList.toggle('hover');">
      <div class="flipper card-1 card">
        <div class="front">
          <!-- front content -->
          <%= image_tag "images/filmsy.png", class: "filmsy-image" %>
          <h4><a href="www.filmsy.top" target="blank" class="hvr-wobble-horizontal">Filmsy</a></h4>
        </div>
        <div class="back">
          <!-- back content -->
          <div class="back-content">
            <br>
            <br>
            <p>A dynamic web app build with Ruby on Rails. Filmsy is an app that provides short films; perfect for people with a busy lifestyle but who are still aching for quality content. Fun feature: users can filter by duration!</p>
          </div>
          <h4><a href="www.filmsy.top" target="blank" class="hvr-wobble-horizontal">Filmsy</a></h4>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flip-container" ontouchstart="this.classList.toggle('hover');">
      <div class="flipper card-1 card">
        <div class="front">
          <!-- front content -->
          <%= image_tag "images/wberoosendaal.png", class: "wbe-image" %>
          <h4><a href="www.wberoosendaal.nl" target="blank" class="hvr-wobble-horizontal">WBE Roosendaal</a></h4>
        </div>
        <div class="back">
          <!-- back content -->
          <div class="back-content">
            <p>Landing page for a Dutch hunting society. The page includes:</p>
            <p>- Clickable map with image enlargement in modal.</p>
            <p>- Simple form with success message after submitting.</p>
            <p>- Album with bootstrap carousel.</p>
            <p>- Media queries: full responsiveness to different screen sizes.</p>
          </div>
          <h4><a href="www.wberoosendaal.nl" target="blank" class="hvr-wobble-horizontal">WBE Roosendaal</a></h4>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
